    // that has length at least |b|.
    // Each append operation can add at most one '1'.
    // The maximum length we might need to consider is |a| + (|a| - 1) = 2*|a| - 1
    // if we append until length |a| + |a| - 1, then remove |a|-1 chars.
    // Or more simply, we can append until the length of 'a' is |b|.
